<div class="section">
  <p>
    MathSoc offers many handy services, both academic and recreational, out of our
    office in MC 3038.  Some things you may find important for classes:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>5&cent; photocopies for those lectures you missed</li>
    <li>Pens and pencils for 25&cent;/each</li>
    <li>Paper (lined and graph) for 10&cent;/10 sheets</li>
    <li>Transparencies for presentations</li>
    <li>Calculators with pink tie stickers for the cheapest on campus</li>
    <li>Staplers to staple your assignment together</li>
    <li>Hole punches</li>
    <li>Work report binding for only 75&cent;!</li>
    <li>Computers with printing for 10&cent; a page</li>
    <li>Locker Signup so you don't have to carry around those heavy books all day</li>
    <li>Textbook library so you have access to material when you don't have your books
        with you.  This includes most first and second year core courses.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    On the recreational side we have a selection of MathNEWS, frisbees, cool math
    novelties and board games for use including:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Cards and cribbage boards</li>
    <li>Settlers</li>
    <li>Carcassonne</li>
    <li>Blockus</li>
    <li>Robo Rally</li>
    <li>Monopoly</li>
    <li>Clue</li>
    <li>Stratego</li>
    <li>Risk</li>
    <li>Ninja Burger</li>
    <li>Munchkin</li>
    <li>And lots more...</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    All these wonderful services are offered to you by volunteers.  If you would like to
    volunteer you can <a href='{$baseUrl}/Office/signup'>signup for your very own office hour</a>
    to help us continue to offer services to the students of UW. If you have any questions or
    concerns we can be contacted by <a href='{$baseUrl}/Contact'>phone</a> or by email at
    {mailto address="office@mathsoc.uwaterloo.ca" encode="javascript_charcode"}.
  </p>
</div>
